Revision history for Email-Send-SMTP-Gmail

0.40    2013/02/11
        Due to lack of response from Net::SMTP::SSL, we added TLS support using Net::SMTP::TLS::ButMaintained
0.33    2013/01/24
        Temporal patch due the issue with RT 81710
0.32    2012/06/29
        Minor improvements
0.30    2012/06/12
        Improvements: use this module with other SMTP servers than Google
0.24    2012/02/02
        Fixbugs and improvements: RT 71864 and 74625
0.01    Date/time
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.
